  <section class="pt-32 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 py-20 text-left">
  <!-- Intro Paragraph -->
  <p class="mb-8 text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800">
    In the ever-evolving landscape of technology, the charitable trust Avanzo stands at the forefront, pioneering a 
    transformative initiative—Cyber Rehabilitation. Rooted in the belief that everyone deserves a chance at redemption 
    and growth, Avanzo has
     embarked on a mission to rehabilitate individuals who have succumbed to the darker aspects of the digital world.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 1 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Understanding Cyber Rehabilitation
  </h2>
  <p class="mb-12 text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    Cyber Rehabilitation is an innovative service designed to assist individuals in overcoming the challenges associated 
    with excessive internet usage, online addiction, and cyber-related misconduct. Avanzo recognizes the pressing need 
    for intervention in a society where the lines between virtual and real life are becoming increasingly blurred. This
     comprehensive program aims to empower individuals to make positive 
    choices, develop healthy online habits, and reintegrate successfully into both the virtual and physical communities.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 2 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Holistic Approach
  </h2>
  <p class="mb-12 text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    At the heart of Avanzo’s Cyber Rehabilitation is a holistic approach that addresses not only the symptoms but also 
    the underlying causes of digital maladaptive behavior. The program encompasses psychological counseling, educational 
    workshops, 
    vocational training, and community support to provide a well-rounded and personalized rehabilitation experience.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 3 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Psychological Counseling
  </h2>
  <p class="mb-12 text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    Experienced psychologists work closely with individuals to identify the root causes of their digital challenges.
     Through one-on-one sessions, participants gain insights into their behavior, learn coping mechanisms, and develop
      strategies to manage stress and anxiety. Avanzo understands the importance
     of mental health in the digital age and strives to create a safe space for individuals to share their struggles.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 4 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Educational Workshops
  </h2>
  <p class="text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    Knowledge is power, and Avanzo ensures that participants are equipped with the skills and awareness needed to 
    navigate the digital world responsibly. Workshops cover topics such as online etiquette, digital literacy, and 
    the potential consequences of cyber misconduct. Participants learn
     to strike a balance between online and offline life, fostering a sense of responsibility in their digital interactions.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 5 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Vocational Training
  </h2>
  <p class="text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    Avanzo believes in the transformative power of education and skill development. The Cyber Rehabilitation program 
    includes vocational training opportunities tailored to the individual’s interests and aptitudes. By acquiring new 
    skills, participants not only enhance their employability but also gain a renewed sense of purpose and accomplishment.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 6 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Community Support
  </h2>
  <p class="text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    The journey to rehabilitation is not a solitary one. Avanzo fosters a sense of community among participants, creating
     a supportive network where individuals can share their experiences, challenges, and triumphs. Group sessions and
      peer support play a crucial
     role in building resilience and reducing the sense of isolation often associated with digital maladaptive behavior.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 7 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Measuring Success
  </h2>
  <p class="text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    Avanzo is committed to measuring the success of its Cyber Rehabilitation program through tangible outcomes such as 
    improved mental well-being, reduced instances of online misconduct, successful reintegration into society, and
     increased employability. 
    Regular assessments and follow-up support ensure that individuals continue to thrive long after completing the program.
  </p>

  <!-- Block 8 -->
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-[Georgia] font-bold text-[#5c4033] mb-4">
    Join Avanzo in Transforming Lives
  </h2>
  <p class="text-lg font-sans leading-relaxed text-gray-800 max-w-3xl">
    Avanzo invites individuals, families, and communities to join hands in creating a digital world where everyone has 
    the opportunity to thrive responsibly. Through Cyber Rehabilitation, Avanzo strives to empower individuals to break
     free from the shackles of online challenges and embrace a future filled with hope, resilience, and positive digital
      engagement. Together, 
    let’s build a society where technology becomes a tool for empowerment and growth, rather than a barrier to well-being.
  </p>
